data.description: Welcome to this breathtaking 4,120 sq ft Pan Abode Cedar Home nestled on a serene one-acre parcel, boasting panoramic views of the majestic Tumwater Mountains. This meticulously crafted 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath home offers a perfect blend of rustic charm and modern comfort, providing a sanctuary for both relaxation and entertaining. The Pana Abode design exudes rich cedar wood creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The 2 bonus rooms and loft are ideal for a home office, fitness area, or hobby room. Enjoy yourselves on the beautiful covered deck during any weather. The detached 3-car garage has ample space for vehicles, tools and storage.  Update: Exterior cleaned, and re-stained ($36,000) and septic pumped.
